<A NAME="Procedures"><H2>Procedures</H2></A>
<P>This section covers the following topics:

<P><A HREF="#NURL">Navigating to URLs</A>
<P><A HREF="#HIST">Displaying the History List</A>
<P><A HREF="#FLIST">Using the Favorites List</A>
<P><A HREF="#STEXT">Searching for Text</A>
<P><A HREF="#PRINTING">Printing</A>

<P><H3><A NAME="NURL">Navigating to URLs</A></H3>
<OL><LI>Click on <IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vurl">.  The URL field appears.  <B>Note: </B>If you don't see the toolbar, press F12 to display it.
<LI>Type the URL you wish to visit.
<LI>Press Enter. </OL>
<P>The NC logo starts spinning. This means that data is being transferred. Three status buttons appear in the upper right browser window. Each button indicates what state the browser is in as it attempts connection with the requested URL.<P>

<UL>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=4>
<TR><TH>If this button lights... </TH><TH>It means... </TH></TR>
<TR><TD>Left  </TD><TD>browser is attempting connection.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Center</TD><TD>browser is connecting to destination.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Right</TD><TD>data transfer is complete.</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
</UL><P>

<P><H3><A NAME="HIST">Displaying the History List</A></H3>
<OL><LI>Click on <IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vmenu"> to display the pop-up menu. 
<LI>Select <B>Navigate -&gt; History list</B>.</OL>
The list of previously viewed pages appears.

<P><H3><A NAME="FLIST">Using the Favorites List</A></H3>
Click on <IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vhots"> to display the Favorites List.
<P>The Favorites List saves your favorite URLs for you.  This list is sometimes referred to as a &quot;Bookmarks&quot; list or &quot;Hotlist.&quot;  The Favorites List lets you visit your favorite Web sites without having to remember the URL.  Use the following steps to customize your Favorites List.

<H4>Adding a URL to the Favorites List</H4>
<OL><LI>Display the page you wish add to your favorites list.
<LI>Click on <IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vhadd"> to add the page.</OL>
The URL is added to your Favorites List.
<P><B>Note:</B> Use the following steps if you are using a television monitor with your NC.
<OL><LI>Display the page you wish add to your favorites list.
<LI>Click on <IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vmenu"> to display the pop-up menu. 
<LI>Select <B>Favorites -&gt; Add page</B>.</OL> 
The current page is added to your Favorites List.

<H4>Removing a URL from the Favorites List</H4>
<OL><LI>Click on <IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vhots"> to display the favorites list.
<LI>Select the URL you wish to delete using the arrow keys or display the page.
<LI>Click on <IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vmenu"> to display the pop-up menu.
<LI>Select <B>Favorites -&gt; Remove page</B>.</OL>
The URL is deleted from your Favorites List.

<P><H3><A NAME="STEXT">Searching for Text</A> </H3>
<OL><LI>Either, click on <IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vfind"> or select <B>Find -&gt; Find text</B> from the pop-up menu to display the text search page.
<LI>Enter the text you wish to search for in the text field.
<LI>Press Enter.</OL>
The current page is scrolled to show the first occurrence of the text string. To find the next occurrence:
<OL><LI>Click on <IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vmenu"> to display the pop-up menu.
<LI>Select <B>Find -&gt; Find text again</B> to display the next match.</OL>

<P><H3><A NAME="PRINTING">Printing</A></H3>
Click on the <IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vprnt"> to print the current page displayed in the browser.

<P><B>Note:</B> Use the following steps if you are using a television monitor with your NC.
<OL><LI>Click on <IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vmenu"> to display the menu. 
<LI>Select the <B>Page -&gt; Print</B> menu item.</OL> 
The current page is printed.<P>

