<A NAME="Toolbar"><H2>Using the Toolbar</H2></A>
<P>The browser Toolbar contains several icons you can click on to access these options:</P>  <B>Note: </B>Toolbar icons noted with * are not displayed if you are using a television monitor with your NC. 

<UL>
<TABLE BORDER = 0><TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vmenu"><TD><B>Menu</B> displays the following menu options:<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Page</B> displays these options: Print, Print options, Stop fetching, and Refresh page.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Edit</B> displays Copy and Paste options.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Navigate</B> displays these navigation options:  Open URL, Home Page, Back, Forward, and History List.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Favorites</B> displays these Favorites List options:  Display, Add, and Remove.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>Find</B> searches for text on the current page.<TR><TD>
<TD><B>View</B> displays these viewing options:  Background, and Images.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vhots"><TD><B>Show Favorites</B> displays your list of favorite URLs.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vhadd">*<TD><B>Add to Favorites</B> adds the current page to your list of favorite URLs.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vprnt">*<TD><B>Print</B> prints the current page.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vprev"><TD><B>Back</B> displays the previous page in the history list.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vnext"><TD><B>Forward</B> displays the next page in the history list.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vhome"><TD><B>Home</B> displays the home page.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vstop"><TD><B>Stop</B> halts the browser from attempting connection to a URL.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vreld"><TD><B>Refresh</B> fetches a new copy of the current page from the server.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vurl"><TD><B>Open URL</B> displays the URL field.  Enter the URL in this line and press Enter to start browser search.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vfind">*<TD><B>Find</B> searches for text within the current page.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vhelp"><TD><B>Help</B> displays this help screen.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=11 SRC="icontype:nc_vup"><IMG WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=11 SRC="icontype:nc_vdown"><TD><B>Page Up/Down</B> moves up/down one screen.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=11 SRC="icontype:nc_vleft"><IMG WIDTH=15 HEIGHT=11 SRC="icontype:nc_vright"><TD><B>Page Left/Right</B> move left/right one screen.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=40 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_nlogo00" WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=32 ><TD><B>NC Logo</B> spins when transferring data.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 SRC="icontype:nc_vstatusg"><IMG WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 SRC="icontype:nc_vstatuso"><IMG WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 SRC="icontype:nc_vstatuso"><TD><B>Connection lights</B> show the state the browser is in as it attempts connection with the requested URL.<TR><TD>
</TABLE></UL>

