<H2><A NAME="Keyboard">Using the Keyboard</A></H2>
<P>You can use the following keyboard shortcuts with the browser:<P>

<UL>
<TABLE BORDER=2 CELLPADDING=4>
<TR><TH>Function  </TH><TH>  Key</TH></TR>
<TR><TD>Display Help </TD><TD> F1</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Display Menu </TD><TD> F2</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Toggle Toolbar on/off </TD><TD> F12</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Print </TD><TD>Ctrl+P</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Copy </TD><TD>Ctrl+C</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Paste </TD><TD>Ctrl+V</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Find Text </TD><TD>Ctrl+F</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Move cursor to next frame </TD><TD>Ctrl+Tab</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Move cursor to previous frame  </TD><TD>Ctrl+Shift+Tab</TD></TR>
</TABLE></UL><P>

