<A NAME="Messages"><H2>Understanding Browser Messages</H2></A>
<P>This section describes error messages you may see while using the browser.

<DL>
<P><DT><B>Unable to send E-mail. </B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  E-mail functionality is unavailable in this version of the browser.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Try using next version of browser.

<P><DT><B>Unable to open this file type.</B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B> The file you are trying to load is not supported in this version of the browser.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Try using next version of browser.

<P><DT><B>Unable to open this type of link.</B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B> This type of link is not supported in this version of the browser.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Try using next version of browser.

<P><DT><B>Unable to find this label.</B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  The Web page contains a link to a non-existent label.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Contact the Web page author.

<P><DT><B>Unable to support authorization type requested by server.</B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  The type of authorization requested by the server is not supported in this version of the browser.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Try using next version of browser.

<P><DT><B>Unable to read cache file.</B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  The file is unavailable or the URL is incorrect.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Verify the URL and retry connection.

<P><DT><B>Unable to locate destination server.</B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  The destination server is unavailable or the URL is incorrect.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Verify URL and retry connection.

<P><DT><B>No data available for this URL.</B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  The destination server is unavailable or the URL is incorrect.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Verify URL and retry connection.

<P><DT><B>Password set for this directory is not accepted by the destination server.</B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  The user details you entered were not reconized by the destination server.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Verify user details and retry connection.

<P><DT><B>Unable to interpret form data.</B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  Web page is unreadable.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Notify the Web page author.

<P><DT><B>Configure the printer driver before printing.</B>   
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  The printer driver must be configured before you can print from your NC.
<DD><B>Action:</B> Select a printer and try again.

<P><DT><B>You are not allowed access to the requested site.</B> 
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  Your NC system administrator has restricted the sites you can access.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Contact your NC system administrator.

<P><DT><B>Caution:  Browser is low on memory. </B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  The browser is running out of available memory.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Contact your NC system administrator if the problem persists.

<P><DT><B>Browser has encountered an internal error.</B> 
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  A internal error has occurred in the browser.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Note the error type and notify your NC system administrator.

<P><DT><B>Browser has insufficient memory to continue...  quitting application.</B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  The browser has run out of available memory.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Contact your NC system administrator if the problem persists.

<P><DT><B>Browser has encountered a fatal internal error ...  quitting application.</B>
<DD><B>Cause:</B>  A fatal internal error has occurred in the browser.
<DD><B>Action:</B>  Note the error type and notify your NC system administrator.
</DL>

